data.description: Now available again – Act quickly, as their misfortune can be your advantage! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home, conveniently situated near the Highway 90 entrance to Lake Forest Subdivision, features a side-entry driveway, a rear-entry double garage, and a full front porch. The dining area's French doors open to a sizable 23 x 19 deck with a privacy panel. The kitchen seamlessly connects to the dining room, creating an inviting open floor plan. A recently renovated half bath is located on the main level. The primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet with spacious storage and a jetted soaker tub/shower combo. The freshly painted living room includes a wood-burning fireplace and a high ceiling with a view of the second story landing. Upstairs, you'll find two additional larger than expected sized bedrooms with ample closet space and a bath. The flooring showcases stunning split brick and hardwoods. The motivated seller underscores a young roof and HVAC system, with ample storage beneath the home.
